N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5329.5 - Reporting of changes

State Regulations

Each operator and sports pool vendor shall have a
continuing duty to disclose any material change or changes in such entity's
business form or activity, information submitted in support of a review
pursuant to section
5329.3
of this Part; information
provided to patrons; information provided to investors; or information provided
in an annual report, or statutory duty to provide information, to the
commission. Notes
